{"tid":801371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵通車】紅雨淹車廠變水城！浸壞轉軌器 列車冇法改道","createTime":"2018-08-31T14:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T01:58:55.000Z","uid":150685,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d332943150338167aada51bdd464fc3436a60968","tid":801371,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535722926_a9e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535722926_a9e5.png&h=f49b7348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前紅雨襲港，高鐵香港段的石崗車廠被洪水倒灌。立法會議員譚文豪今日再取得一批車廠內部相片，可見部分路軌嚴重水浸。譚引述消息稱，該石崗路段負責轉換路軌的路軌轉轍器，在暴雨中被浸壞，要即時更換，他擔心若高鐵通車後，路軌轉轍器再次因下雨故障，如列車駛向錯誤方向，後果或不堪設想。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪指，從相片中可見，銀白色正方型的部件即為路軌轉轍器，部件內有電動摩打，可以操控路軌改道，據他所知，該路軌轉轍器在紅雨當日，因去水設計出問題被浸壞，令控制室無法控制列車改道。譚認為當日並非百年一遇的大豪雨，但高鐵設計竟然連紅雨考驗都無法通過，明顯是重大缺失，港鐵仍辯稱事件不影響高鐵通車日期。他促港鐵交待在今次紅雨下，車廠共有多少部件損壞及涉的維修費。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》亦接獲消息人士舉報，指紅雨當日車廠內有多處水浸，包括主大樓消防泵房，水深達一呎以上；車輪檢測器在水浸後完全失靈，暫不能監測車輪狀況；有蓋維修車庫有軌道如「河流」般嚴重水浸；控制中心有電子儀器房嚴重滲水；但車廠內沙包嚴重不足，即使手動抽水泵亦只有數個，根本不足以應付豪雨。從讀者提供的相片可見，一段路軌嚴重水浸，流水湧入路軌中央，車廠主大樓消防泵房亦嚴重水浸。《蘋果》向港鐵查詢，但暫未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535720309_55d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535720309_55d0.jpg&h=227766b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車廠的有蓋維修車庫，有軌道如「河流」般嚴重水浸。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535720309_728c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535720309_728c.jpg&h=d708824b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車廠主大樓消防泵房，水深達一呎以上。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535720362_6576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535720362_6576.jpg&h=292e8094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚文豪指，高鐵路軌的去水設計，竟連紅色暴雨的考驗都無法通過，明顯是重大缺失。譚文豪提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535720362_9ba2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535720362_9ba2.jpg&h=641cdf65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銀白色正方型為高鐵列車轉軌器，內有電動摩打，可操控列車改道，疑因去水設計缺憾，日前被浸壞，令控制室無法控制列車改道。譚文豪提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180831/58631073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58631073&d=wlg5qpysbMwI8blMwSHqzXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=03060445\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58631073&h=462f3c81\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180831/58631073</a>"},{"pid":"b9a11e3683defed3a8d000305468e628e95bcbc2","tid":801371,"uid":150685,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人好期待通車日落大雨"},{"pid":"c487de35e020ba39f4fb665cd39a032e0160ff59","tid":801371,"uid":66527,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"真係估中左會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6b77bbf0ac05ee55f7c0324edee23c860988b0","tid":801371,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b9a11e3683defed3a8d000305468e628e95bcbc2","tid":801371,"uid":150685,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人好期待通車日落大雨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:45:46.000Z","msg":"天文台話未來9日都落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ce495116769031022307363c78c00cd336455b","tid":801371,"uid":39601,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"通車打8號波或者黑雨唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631879f1fa9681e4a2593a06719a36906b74e2b5","tid":801371,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"27ce495116769031022307363c78c00cd336455b","tid":801371,"uid":39601,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"通車打8號波或者黑雨唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"但天文台係只會掛黃雨<br />\n<br />\n話知你高鐵地底3層全浸, 支那狗關員浸到發漲一條條浮屍<br />\n<br />\n天文台都係會一直堅持落去"},{"pid":"608d67e05b7a241f119a32c320a805d477a5bcdd","tid":801371,"uid":22116,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535720309_55d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535720309_55d0.jpg&h=227766b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20091115/photo/1115-00282-013b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20091115%2Fphoto%2F1115-00282-013b2.jpg&h=bfb40b5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2143b88219537661c512827993c6ef811650392","tid":801371,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:51:23.000Z","msg":"每小時50毫米都頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48c3da8abd64a39a7e747d54aecef9ff975f906","tid":801371,"uid":64571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"正確啲講只係黃雨"},{"pid":"4128b96e27a20af51ac